sources.description: Title: La morte viene dallo spazio Summary: Scientists discover that a group of meteors are hurtling on a collison course with Earth, and if they hit, the planet will be destroyed. Directed by: Paolo Heusch, Mario Bava Actors: Production Company: Royal Film Release Date: 27 September 1961 (USA) Aspect Ratio: REMOVE_TAG Scientists discover that a group of meteors are hurtling on a collison course with Earth, and if they hit, the planet will be destroyed.
